  "description": "<h2><u>C&amp;S Coordinator (LTA Projects)</u></h2>\n<p><u><strong>Visit www.ppsjob.com.sg</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>· Liaise, coordinate, challenge, find solutions with Consultants QPD, AC, QPS and LTA team for the LTA Project</p>\n<p>· Review shop drawings such as (Piling, Structures, Formwork</p>\n<p>· Liaise with sub-con design team for design clearance</p>\n<p>· Liaise with Authorities to reply and obtain Authority clearances such as BCA and other relevant authorities</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Qualifications</p>\n<p>· At least Degree in Civil Engineering</p>\n<p>· Minimum 3 years experience preferably in LTA projects</p>\n<p>· Experience in Design Consultancy will be advantage</p>\n<p>Able to handle AC, QPD and QPS in design construction</p>",
